{"id":360115,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/46/12/461250.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"班固米做菜人","groupHref":"/group/zuocai","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/43/4324.jpg?r=1574965416","message":"因为疫情很久没去大超市，昨天正好办事路过Real就把无人问津的生猪耳包圆儿了。<br>做法很简单，猪耳洗净冷水下锅，加葱姜啤酒煮开3分钟，捞出来再清洗之后剪成条状；起锅热油加葱姜蒜炒香，下剪好的猪耳加老抽上色，再加开水香料、糖盐，煮开后转小火卤50分钟。<br>忘了买啤酒只能用家里的Radler（柠檬啤）凑合，味道也还行<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">没觉出来酸</span><br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/3dOxDJHfjMY8sU6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/11/28/3dOxDJHfjMY8sU6.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">隔壁的穆斯林大哥馋哭了</span> ","time":"2020-11-28 23:04","title":"卤猪耳","userId":"aerbioer","userName":"aerbioer","userSign":"(宿題は8月32日に)"}